---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Points Beyond AI"
  description="Privacy policy for Points Beyond AI. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonical="https://pointsbeyond.ai/privacy/"
>
  <div class="section container prose">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 27, 2026</p>

    <p>Points Beyond LLC ("Points Beyond AI," "we," "our," or "us") operates the website at pointsbeyond.ai and provides AI voice agent, reputation management, and answer engine optimization services. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding it.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email address, phone number, and website URL submitted through contact forms</li>
      <li>Service interest selections and message content submitted through forms</li>
      <li>SMS consent status when you opt in to text communications</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We may also collect standard web analytics data (pages visited, referral source, browser type) through analytics tools. This data is aggregated and not linked to your identity.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your inquiry and schedule your strategy call</li>
      <li>To deliver the services you've engaged us to provide</li>
      <li>To send transactional emails and SMS messages related to your account or inquiry</li>
      <li>To improve our website and service offerings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <div class="sms-block">
      <h2>SMS Communications &amp; TCPA Compliance</h2>
      <p><strong>No mobile information will be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes.</strong> All other categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.</p>
      <p>By providing your phone number and checking the SMS consent box on our contact form, you consent to receive text messages from Points Beyond AI regarding your inquiry and our services. Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency varies based on your inquiry.</p>
      <p><strong>To opt out:</strong> Reply STOP to any message you receive from us. You will be removed from all SMS communications immediately. Reply HELP for assistance.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share your information only in the following limited circumstances:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> We use third-party tools (such as form processors and email platforms) to operate our business. These providers access your information only to perform services on our behalf and are bound by confidentiality obligations.</li>
      <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law or in response to a valid legal request.</li>
      <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> If Points Beyond LLC is acquired or merges with another entity, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain contact form submissions and inquiry data for up to 24 months, or longer if an active client relationship exists. You may request deletion of your data at any time (see Your Rights below).</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Our website may use cookies for basic functionality and analytics. We do not use cookies for targeted advertising. You can disable cookies in your browser settings; some site features may not function as intended if you do.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request a copy of the personal information we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
      <li>Opt out of SMS communications at any time by replying STOP</li>
      <li>Opt out of email communications by using the unsubscribe link in any email we send</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@pointsbeyond.ai">info@pointsbeyond.ai</a>.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our services are directed at businesses and business owners. We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under 18 years of age.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy periodically. When we do, we'll update the "Last updated" date above. Material changes will be communicated via email to active clients.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Points Beyond LLC<br />
    Fairfax County, Virginia<br />
    <a href="mailto:info@pointsbeyond.ai">info@pointsbeyond.ai</a></p>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 720px;
    padding-block: var(--section-padding);
  }

  .prose h1 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .prose ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .prose ul li {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .prose ul li::before {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .sms-block {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    margin-block: 2rem;
  }

  .sms-block h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sms-block {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
